    <item>
      <title>Bigger Truth</title>
      <link>https://stwi.blog/waking-up/blue_work/truth/</link>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Apr 2022 15:26:15 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://stwi.blog/waking-up/blue_work/truth/</guid>
      <description>How do we know something is True? This is such an important, fundamental question and yet I don’t see people thinking about it. I used to believe that only rationality could get me to Truth. Now I realize that while I will always honor and cherish my rationality, it is only one path to Truth. There are others.
In my mid thirties, I developed a very dangerous, painful tumor in my spinal column.</description>
